content: Hello Jeyachandran! It's nice to meet you. I'm Master, the hiring officer for the Software Engineer position at Google. I must say, your resume looks very impressive. You have a strong background in web development, with experience working with various technologies such as React.js, Node.js, and MongoDB. Can you tell me a little bit about your experience as a web developer at Fabromant? What kind of projects did you work on, and what were some of your responsibilities in that role?
